nodes.text: Palm fruit was a food that could be fried. Resistance spy Vi Moradi ate and enjoyed palm fruit while living on her homeworld of Chaaktil. The fruit, which was edible by members of the human species, was one of the details that Moradi mentioned while describing her homeworld to Salju, the owner of a filling station on the planet Batuu in 34 ABY
Palm fruit was mentioned in Delilah S. Dawson's 2019 novel Galaxy's Edge: Black Spire.
